-- IMF’S Cottarelli Sees Risk of Over-Tightening Fiscal Policy
-- B y   S a n d r i n e   R a s t e l l o
-- 2012-01-24T15:30:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/imf-s-cottarelli-sees-risk-of-over-tightening-fiscal-policy.html
The International Monetary Fund
cautioned against cutting budget deficits too fast as global
economic growth slows.  “Fiscal adjustment should continue but should continue at
the right pace,”  Carlo Cottarelli , who heads the IMF fiscal
affairs department, told reporters today in  Washington .  To contact the reporter on this story:
